# Service Definitions

Port 2
Protocol 2


# Logging Facility

SyslogFacility AUTHPRIV

# Authentication

LoginGraceTime 2m
PermitRootLogin without-password
StrictModes yes
MaxAuthTries 3

RSAAuthentication yes  # Allow RSA key Authentication
PubkeyAuthentication yes # Allow Public Key Authentication
AuthorizedKeysFile .ssh/authorized_keys # Define the file required
PermitEmptyPasswords no # Do NOT allow empty passwords
PasswordAuthentication no # Require password authentication via KEY only
